ningen ogs\u00e5 for dem som er deres n\u00e6rmeste. Men det er s\u00e5 feil. For familie og venner er det utrolig belastende \u00e5 sitte igjen etter et selvmord, sier hun."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c02d6da4506e04e443ff0825bf40fc6074a64723679a4e7f591ea476609b6447"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-10-29T05:23:49.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Langt flere d\u00f8r etter selvmord enn i trafikkulykker. \u2013 Vi m\u00e5 v\u00e5ge \u00e5 stille sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5let: \u00abTenker du p\u00e5 \u00e5 ta selvmord\u00bb, r\u00e5der ekspert."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article13708742.ece/ojnsnl/ALTERNATES/w980-default/20161020_RichardSagen_SverreVangstad_uke-8278.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/428490f7f920acf703224b0e820ae42734d7b65b.jpg?5999ac5b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Du kan aldri plante en tanke om selvmord -adressa.no", "Se etter tegn", "Flest menn", "Redd for \u00e5 si fra"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "428490f7f920acf703224b0e820ae42734d7b65b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Helse"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Helse"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["selvmord", "tenke", "traumatisk stress"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["sverre", "folkehelseinstituttet", "leve", "ressurssenter", "ukeadressa"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["midt-norge", "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["bente espeland", "rita sm\u00e5vik", "hilde-carin storhaug", "lena-marie haugerud"]}, {"field": "kw-sentiment",